  <brief_title>Validation of a Questionnaire to Identify Signs and Symptoms of Nephrogenic Systemic Fibrosis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Validation of a Questionnaire as a Screening Tool to Identify Signs and Symptoms of Nephrogenic Systemic Fibrosis</official_title>
  <sponsors>
