  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The Primary Aim of this study is to validate a questionnaire as a screening tool to identify
      subjects with symptoms suggestive of nephrogenic systemic fibrosis (NSF). The investigators
      believe that there will be difference between subjects with NSF and other skin conditions and
      normal skin.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
